::Aerotaur::
       "Are you stupid or just brain-dead?  I haven't even seen my commanders 
since before the battle.  Thus, no command."  He glares harder but puts away 
his guns.  "I'm here because I don't leave a job half done.  My objective was 
to keep her alive, so that's what I intend to do."
